  <sect3 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Four In a Row</title>

    <para>
      <application>four-in-a-row</application> is a
      strategy game for <application>GNOME</application>.
      The aim of the game is to stack four of your marbles in a horizontal, 
      vertical or diagonal line while stopping your opponent 
      from doing the same with their marbles.
    </para>

    &lfs76_checked;

